Prayer of the Rollerboys;;1990;;R;;Action,Crime,Drama;;5.6;;Rick King;;Corey Haim,Patricia Arquette,Christopher Collet,Julius Harris,Devin Clark,Mark Pellegrino,Morgan Weisser,Jake Dengel,G. Smokey Campbell,John P. Connolly,J.C. Quinn,Trevor Eyster,Aron Eisenberg,Joel Bott,Doug Boyce,Chad Bruechart,Mike Colabella,Tim Dennis;;Set in an unspecified time in the future, USA has declined and become a country of violence and racial prejudice. Griffin earns his living delivering pizzas while he tries to take care of his little brother. An old friend of his, Gary Lee, is the leader of a gang with big ambitions, the Rollerboys. Griff joins them to help the police keep track of the gang.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0102703/